[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 8.18,
    "text": "I'm Ricky Carmichael. I'm a native Floridian and I'm here to conquer Florida."
  },
  {
    "start": 8.18,
    "end": 20.48,
    "text": "All right man heading to OWC. Yeah Orlando water sports complex. I've always heard a lot of cool"
  },
  {
    "start": 20.48,
    "end": 27.04,
    "text": "stuff as long as I've lived in Florida. I've never been to OWC. There's many times we've passed it."
  },
  {
    "start": 27.04,
    "end": 32.24,
    "text": "Yeah passed it so many times but I've never ridden a cable park. What about tricks? What do you got"
  },
  {
    "start": 32.24,
    "end": 37.92,
    "text": "left in your bag? You know I can hold my own. A sticking ball guy like you probably would really"
  },
  {
    "start": 37.92,
    "end": 46.3,
    "text": "struggle. I've done a lot of wakeboarding after I was done riding motorcycles. I'd always hop on"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.3,
    "end": 51.42,
    "text": "my boat and go out for a little wakeboard ride but to be able to do it at a cable park here"
  },
  {
    "start": 51.42,
    "end": 55.48,
    "text": "was awesome. Come on over here Caden. There you go. Look look look."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.04,
    "end": 63.1,
    "text": "All right. Good to see you man. You doing all right?"
  },
  {
    "start": 70.24,
    "end": 73.54,
    "text": "Dude I've never been here. First time? Yeah first time."
  },
  {
    "start": 75.0,
    "end": 76.2,
    "text": "Ah nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 77.48,
    "end": 86.9,
    "text": "Being the company today of"
  },
  {
    "start": 86.9,
    "end": 87.02,
    "text": "Jets."
  },
  {
    "start": 87.04,
    "end": 92.2,
    "text": "Sean Murray and Danny Harf was awesome. To see them in their environment is always mind-blowing."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.2,
    "end": 94.98,
    "text": "But see I'm lucky they're giving me tips right?"
  },
  {
    "start": 94.98,
    "end": 95.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 95.98,
    "end": 96.98,
    "text": "Woo!"
  },
  {
    "start": 117.04,
    "end": 128.98,
    "text": "So what's the plan over here? You went through some buoys that's cool. Yeah you managed to get off the platform but this is conquering Florida. See that jump out there? Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 128.98,
    "end": 135.98,
    "text": "You got that? I don't know. We'll give it a try. I'm a little nervous but if I do that and I land it you have to try it."
  },
  {
    "start": 135.98,
    "end": 141.48,
    "text": "The jump? Yes. Whoa! Whoa! Yes. Yes. Let's worry about me getting off the water first."
  },
  {
    "start": 141.48,
    "end": 141.98,
    "text": "Haha."
  },
  {
    "start": 141.98,
    "end": 142.98,
    "text": "But you're going to get out."
  },
  {
    "start": 142.98,
    "end": 144.98,
    "text": "And I'm going to have to wait and see."
  },
  {
    "start": 144.98,
    "end": 146.98,
    "text": "We're going to have to wait and see."
  },
  {
    "start": 146.98,
    "end": 148.98,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "start": 148.98,
    "end": 153.98,
    "text": "J.H. was sleeping on my skills like he always does. I said you know if I grease this thing I get three attempts to grease it. If I do then you have to go out there and do it."
  },
  {
    "start": 153.98,
    "end": 154.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 154.98,
    "end": 155.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 155.98,
    "end": 156.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 156.98,
    "end": 157.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 157.98,
    "end": 158.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 158.98,
    "end": 159.98,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 159.98,
    "end": 160.98,
    "text": "Woo hoo!"
  },
  {
    "start": 160.98,
    "end": 162.98,
    "text": "Woo hoo!"
  },
  {
    "start": 162.98,
    "end": 164.98,
    "text": "Well long story short I fulfilled my end of the bet."
  },
  {
    "start": 164.98,
    "end": 166.98,
    "text": "This is going to be good right here."
  },
  {
    "start": 166.98,
    "end": 167.98,
    "text": "Haha."
  },
  {
    "start": 167.98,
    "end": 168.98,
    "text": "Hahaha."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.98,
    "end": 170.98,
    "text": "We'll try not to go face forward right here."
  },
  {
    "start": 170.98,
    "end": 171.98,
    "text": "Woo hoo."
  },
  {
    "start": 171.98,
    "end": 172.98,
    "text": "See ya!"
  },
  {
    "start": 172.98,
    "end": 174.98,
    "text": "Oh, he got it!"
  },
  {
    "start": 174.98,
    "end": 175.98,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "start": 179.98,
    "end": 182.98,
    "text": "J.H. couldn't even make it to the ramp, so..."
  },
  {
    "start": 182.98,
    "end": 184.98,
    "text": "Go, go, get up! Get up!"
  },
  {
    "start": 189.98,
    "end": 192.98,
    "text": "You don't get up this time, the bet's off."
  },
  {
    "start": 192.98,
    "end": 194.98,
    "text": "And you gotta ride in a tube the rest of the day."
  },
  {
    "start": 194.98,
    "end": 197.98,
    "text": "Good luck. Stand up. Forward, forward!"
  },
  {
    "start": 197.98,
    "end": 198.98,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "start": 198.98,
    "end": 199.98,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "start": 199.98,
    "end": 202.98,
    "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh!"
  },
  {
    "start": 204.98,
    "end": 206.98,
    "text": "Tube for you the rest of the day."
  },
  {
    "start": 206.98,
    "end": 207.98,
    "text": "Did that count?"
  },
  {
    "start": 207.98,
    "end": 208.98,
    "text": "No, that... dude."
  },
  {
    "start": 208.98,
    "end": 209.98,
    "text": "That was close!"
  },
  {
    "start": 209.98,
    "end": 211.98,
    "text": "No, not really."
  },
  {
    "start": 214.98,
    "end": 218.98,
    "text": "I was so excited to have the chance to come to OWC today,"
  },
  {
    "start": 218.98,
    "end": 220.98,
    "text": "Orlando's Water Sports Complex."
  },
  {
    "start": 222.98,
    "end": 225.98,
    "text": "Such a fun time, and it met all my expectations."
  },
  {
